{"tid":1297332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地應杯葛所有港產警匪片","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:15:25.000Z","uid":244845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14b3d092a1282178d4b2bd7e96f597a89ca5c182","tid":1297332,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"呢個幾月既洗禮 我諗差佬腐敗既形像都好根深蒂固<br />\n<br />\n為左令佢地呢個形像永不翻身<br />\n我地要杯葛所有港產警匪片<br />\n原因為一般警匪片都會將條差佬講成一個好撚正義 為民服務既人<br />\n雖然係電影 但真係會有觀眾 睇完後潛而墨化左 相信真係會有一個咁撚正義既死差佬<br />\n<br />\n暑假檔期就快到 我知好多巴絲都唔會睇港產片 由期係警匪片 <br />\n不過可能你地既父母/ 後輩會有定期入戲院睇戲既習慣<br />\n如果知道你地父母/朋友想入戲院睇警匪片<br />\n我地應該呼籲佢地遠離呢啲有毒電影"},{"pid":"836b559bc03a6e1418e2b61dfbb828c1aa67e36b","tid":1297332,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"我要律師"},{"pid":"2ca3d0424241f8d788bba583fb3827e051da9edc","tid":1297332,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3f767233b738b0ac25f3740a6160338796572a","tid":1297332,"uid":33694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"匪匪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f6fdc00a06548bfde20f659a1a041dea293f9b","tid":1297332,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f3f767233b738b0ac25f3740a6160338796572a","tid":1297332,"uid":33694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"匪匪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549b8be237418e5704381d8c3de74c0b9cbef563","tid":1297332,"uid":148673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,